<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Interspousal Transfer Deed - California</title>
    <style>
        @page { size: letter; margin: 0.5in 0.625in 0.625in 0.75in; }
        @media print { body { -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; print-color-adjust: exact; } }
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body { font-family: "Times New Roman", Times, serif; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 1.4; color: #000; background: #fff; }
        .deed-page { width: 100%; min-height: 100%; }
        .header-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 3.5in; gap: 0.25in; margin-bottom: 0.15in; min-height: 2in; }
        .recording-info { font-size: 10pt; line-height: 1.35; }
        .recording-info-label { font-weight: bold; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 9pt; letter-spacing: 0.5px; margin-bottom: 2px; }
        .recording-info-value { margin-bottom: 0.12in; }
        .recorder-space { border: 2px solid #000; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: flex-start; padding-top: 0.15in; min-height: 2in; }
        .recorder-space-label { font-size: 8pt; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; color: #000; text-align: center; font-weight: bold; }
        .reference-line { display: flex; justify-content: flex-end; gap: 0.4in; font-size: 10pt; margin-bottom: 0.1in; padding-bottom: 0.08in; border-bottom: 1px solid #000; }
        .reference-item { white-space: nowrap; }
        .reference-label { font-weight: bold; }
        .deed-title { text-align: center; font-size: 18pt; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; margin: 0.2in 0; padding: 0.1in 0; }
        .exemption-notice { margin: 0.15in 0; padding: 0.12in; border: 2px solid #000; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 1.4; }
        .exemption-header { font-weight: bold; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 0.08in; }
        .exemption-cite { font-style: italic; font-size: 9pt; margin-top: 0.05in; }
        .deed-body { margin: 0.15in 0; text-align: justify; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 1.45; }
        .deed-body p { margin-bottom: 0.12in; }
        .party-name { font-weight: bold; text-transform: uppercase; }
        .party-designation { font-style: normal; }
        .grant-language { text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: bold; }
        .county-name { font-weight: bold; text-transform: uppercase; border-bottom: 1px solid #000; padding: 0 0.1in; }
        .spousal-declaration { margin: 0.15in 0; padding: 0.12in; border: 1px solid #000; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 1.4; }
        .legal-description-section { margin: 0.15in 0; page-break-inside: avoid; }
        .legal-description-content { font-size: 11pt; line-height: 1.45; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap; }
        .legal-description-exhibit-ref { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }
        .apn-line { margin-top: 0.12in; font-size: 11pt; }
        .apn-label { font-weight: bold; }
        .apn-value { font-family: "Courier New", Courier, monospace; letter-spacing: 1px; }
        .execution-section { margin-top: 0.25in; page-break-inside: avoid; }
        .execution-date { margin-bottom: 0.2in; font-size: 12pt; }
        .date-label { font-weight: bold; }
        .date-value { border-bottom: 1px solid #000; padding: 0 0.15in; min-width: 2.5in; display: inline-block; }
        .signature-block { margin-top: 0.3in; }
        .signature-entry { margin-bottom: 0.3in; }
        .signature-line { border-bottom: 1px solid #000; width: 3.5in; height: 0.3in; }
        .signature-name { font-size: 11pt; margin-top: 0.05in; text-transform: uppercase; }
        .notary-section { margin-top: 0.3in; page-break-inside: avoid; border-top: 2px solid #000; padding-top: 0.15in; }
        .notary-disclaimer { font-size: 8pt; font-style: italic; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.3; margin-bottom: 0.15in; padding: 0.1in; border: 1px solid #000; }
        .notary-title { text-align: center; font-weight: bold; font-size: 10pt; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 2px; margin-bottom: 0.1in; }
        .notary-venue { font-size: 10pt; margin-bottom: 0.1in; line-height: 1.5; }
        .venue-line { display: flex; align-items: center; }
        .venue-state { width: 2.5in; }
        .venue-bracket { font-size: 14pt; }
        .venue-ss { margin-left: 0.3in; font-size: 9pt; }
        .county-field { border-bottom: 1px solid #000; min-width: 1.8in; display: inline-block; padding: 0 0.1in; }
        .notary-body { font-size: 10pt; line-height: 1.5; text-align: justify; margin: 0.1in 0; }
        .notary-body p { margin-bottom: 0.1in; }
        .notary-field { border-bottom: 1px solid #000; min-width: 1.2in; display: inline-block; padding: 0 0.05in; }
        .notary-field.long { min-width: 2in; }
        .notary-certification { margin-top: 0.1in; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 1.4; }
        .notary-witness { margin-top: 0.15in; font-weight: bold; font-size: 10pt; }
        .notary-execution { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 2in; gap: 0.4in; margin-top: 0.2in; align-items: end; }
        .notary-signature-line { border-bottom: 1px solid #000; width: 2.8in; height: 0.25in; }
        .notary-signature-label { font-size: 9pt; margin-top: 0.05in; }
        .notary-print-name { margin-top: 0.1in; font-size: 9pt; }
        .notary-commission { margin-top: 0.1in; font-size: 9pt; }
        .commission-field { border-bottom: 1px solid #000; min-width: 1.2in; display: inline-block; }
        .notary-seal-area { border: 2px solid #000; width: 2in; height: 2in; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; text-align: center; }
        .seal-label { font-size: 9pt; font-weight: bold; text-transform: uppercase; color: #666; }
        .page-break { page-break-before: always; }
        .exhibit-page { padding-top: 0.5in; }
        .exhibit-header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0.4in; }
        .exhibit-title { font-size: 16pt; font-weight: bold; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 2px; }
        .exhibit-subtitle { font-size: 12pt; margin-top: 0.1in; font-style: italic; }
        .exhibit-content { font-size: 11pt; line-height: 1.6; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap; }
        .exhibit-apn { margin-top: 0.3in; font-size: 10pt; border-top: 1px solid #ccc; padding-top: 0.15in; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="deed-page">
        <div class="header-grid">
            <div class="recording-info">
                <div class="recording-info-label">Recording Requested By:</div>
                <div class="recording-info-value">{{ requested_by or title_company or '' }}</div>
                <div class="recording-info-label">When Recorded Mail To:</div>
                <div class="recording-info-value">
                    {% if return_to %}
                        {% if return_to.get('name') %}{{ return_to.get('name') }}<br>{% endif %}
                        {% if return_to.get('company') %}{{ return_to.get('company') }}<br>{% endif %}
                        {% if return_to.get('address1') %}{{ return_to.get('address1') }}<br>{% endif %}
                        {% if return_to.get('address2') %}{{ return_to.get('address2') }}<br>{% endif %}
                        {% set _city = return_to.get('city', '') %}{% set _state = return_to.get('state', '') %}{% set _zip = return_to.get('zip', '') %}
                        {% if _city or _state or _zip %}{{ _city }}{% if _city and (_state or _zip) %}, {% endif %}{{ _state }} {{ _zip }}{% endif %}
                    {% else %}_________________________________<br>_________________________________{% endif %}
                </div>
                <div class="recording-info-label">Mail Tax Statements To:</div>
                <div class="recording-info-value">{% if mail_tax_to %}{{ mail_tax_to }}{% else %}Same as above{% endif %}</div>
            </div>
            <div class="recorder-space">
                <div class="recorder-space-label">Space Above This Line<br>For Recorder's Use Only</div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="reference-line">
            {% if apn %}<span class="reference-item"><span class="reference-label">APN:</span> {{ apn }}</span>{% endif %}
            {% if title_order_no %}<span class="reference-item"><span class="reference-label">Order No:</span> {{ title_order_no }}</span>{% endif %}
            {% if escrow_no %}<span class="reference-item"><span class="reference-label">Escrow No:</span> {{ escrow_no }}</span>{% endif %}
        </div>

        <h1 class="deed-title">Interspousal Transfer Deed</h1>

        <div class="exemption-notice">
            <div class="exemption-header">Documentary Transfer Tax: Exempt</div>
            <div>This transfer is exempt from Documentary Transfer Tax pursuant to California Revenue and Taxation Code Section 11927 (transfer between spouses).</div>
            {% if dtt_exempt_reason %}<div style="margin-top:0.05in;">Additional basis: {{ dtt_exempt_reason }}</div>{% endif %}
            <div class="exemption-cite">R&T Code ยง11927</div>
        </div>

        <div class="deed-body">
            <p>FOR VALUABLE CONSIDERATION, receipt of which is hereby acknowledged, and pursuant to a transmutation agreement between the undersigned spouses,</p>
            <p><span class="party-name">{{ grantors_text or '_______________________________________' }}</span> <span class="party-designation">("Transferor Spouse")</span></p>
            <p>hereby <span class="grant-language">GRANTS AND TRANSFERS</span> to</p>
            <p><span class="party-name">{{ grantees_text or '_______________________________________' }}</span> <span class="party-designation">("Transferee Spouse")</span></p>
            <p>all right, title and interest in and to the following described real property in the County of <span class="county-name">{{ county or '_______________' }}</span>, State of California:</p>
        </div>

        <div class="legal-description-section">
            {% if legal_description and legal_description|length > (exhibit_threshold or 600) %}
                <p class="legal-description-exhibit-ref">See Exhibit "A" attached hereto and incorporated herein by this reference.</p>
            {% else %}
                <div class="legal-description-content">{{ legal_description or 'LEGAL DESCRIPTION TO BE INSERTED' }}</div>
            {% endif %}
            {% if apn %}<div class="apn-line"><span class="apn-label">Assessor's Parcel Number:</span> <span class="apn-value">{{ apn }}</span></div>{% endif %}
        </div>

        <div class="spousal-declaration">
            The undersigned Transferor Spouse declares under penalty of perjury that: (1) Transferor and Transferee are legally married spouses; (2) This transfer is made with the express intent to change the character of the above-described property{% if vesting %} to {{ vesting }}{% endif %}; and (3) This deed constitutes a valid transmutation agreement pursuant to California Family Code Section 850 et seq.
        </div>

        <div class="execution-section">
            <div class="execution-date"><span class="date-label">Dated:</span> <span class="date-value">{{ execution_date or now().strftime('%B %d, %Y') }}</span></div>
            <div class="signature-block">
                {% set signers = grantors_text.split(';') if grantors_text and ';' in grantors_text else [grantors_text] if grantors_text else [] %}
                {% for signer in signers %}{% set signer_name = signer.strip() if signer else '' %}{% if signer_name %}
                <div class="signature-entry"><div class="signature-line"></div><div class="signature-name">{{ signer_name }}</div></div>
                {% endif %}{% endfor %}
                {% if not signers or signers|length == 0 %}<div class="signature-entry"><div class="signature-line"></div><div class="signature-name">Transferor Spouse</div></div>{% endif %}
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="notary-section">
            <div class="notary-disclaimer">A notary public or other officer completing this certificate verifies only the identity of the individual who signed the document to which this certificate is attached, and not the truthfulness, accuracy, or validity of that document.</div>
            <div class="notary-title">Acknowledgment</div>
            <div class="notary-venue">
                <div class="venue-line"><span class="venue-state">State of California</span><span class="venue-bracket">)</span></div>
                <div class="venue-line"><span class="venue-state"></span><span class="venue-bracket">)</span><span class="venue-ss">ss.</span></div>
                <div class="venue-line"><span class="venue-state">County of <span class="county-field">{{ county or '' }}</span></span><span class="venue-bracket">)</span></div>
            </div>
            <div class="notary-body">
                <p>On <span class="notary-field">______________</span> before me, <span class="notary-field long">_________________________</span>, a Notary Public, personally appeared <span class="notary-field long">{{ grantors_text or '_________________________' }}</span>, who proved to me on the basis of satisfactory evidence to be the person(s) whose name(s) is/are subscribed to the within instrument and acknowledged to me that he/she/they executed the same in his/her/their authorized capacity(ies), and that by his/her/their signature(s) on the instrument the person(s), or the entity upon behalf of which the person(s) acted, executed the instrument.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="notary-certification">I certify under PENALTY OF PERJURY under the laws of the State of California that the foregoing paragraph is true and correct.</div>
            <div class="notary-witness">WITNESS my hand and official seal.</div>
            <div class="notary-execution">
                <div>
                    <div class="notary-signature-line"></div>
                    <div class="notary-signature-label">Signature of Notary Public</div>
                    <div class="notary-print-name">Name (Printed): <span class="notary-field">___________________</span></div>
                    <div class="notary-commission">My Commission Expires: <span class="commission-field">___________</span></div>
                </div>
                <div class="notary-seal-area"><span class="seal-label">Place Notary Seal Above</span></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    {% if legal_description and legal_description|length > (exhibit_threshold or 600) %}
    <div class="page-break"></div>
    <div class="exhibit-page">
        <div class="exhibit-header">
            <div class="exhibit-title">Exhibit "A"</div>
            <div class="exhibit-subtitle">Legal Description</div>
        </div>
        <div class="exhibit-content">{{ legal_description }}</div>
        {% if apn %}<div class="exhibit-apn"><span class="apn-label">APN:</span> <span class="apn-value">{{ apn }}</span></div>{% endif %}
    </div>
    {% endif %}

    {# PAGE 2 (or 3): CALIFORNIA ALL-PURPOSE ACKNOWLEDGMENT - Civil Code ยง 1189 #}
    {% set document_title = 'Interspousal Transfer Deed' %}
    {% include '_partials/notary_acknowledgment.jinja2' %}
</body>
</html>
